      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies. This example delivers a visceral driving experience with a 7,900 RPM redline and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul and structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by a functional variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This is a robust, performance-oriented specimen with a clean power band and precise steering rack feedback, perfect for the dedicated enthusiast.",
